<figureCitation box="[1262,1343,834,859]" captionStart="FIGURE 15" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1895,1917]" captionTargetBox="[172,1431,1003,1837]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[158,1443,993,1848]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 15. Stirellus multipunctatus sp. nov. Male. A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: face." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/255866/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="120">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
A).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
